"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-life-style-fashion-coco-gauff-olympians-paris-instagram-milan-b2585049.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 321, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  As athletes get into ready position for theParis2024 Olympics, which commences this Friday, we take a look at some of the most fashionable stars when they arenotin their element.\", \"from\": 322, \"to\": 524, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"1.\", \"from\": 526, \"to\": 528, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Alica Schmidt, Athletics  German sprinter, Alica Schmidt, has got hearts racing beyond the track.\", \"from\": 529, \"to\": 626, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 529, \"end\": 542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alica_Schmidt\", \"score\": 0.9999999993119673, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alica Schmidt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alica_Schmidt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alica_Schmidt\"}, {\"begin\": 555, \"end\": 561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"score\": 0.9049127878534888, \"rank\": 0.10433524363392242, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\"}, {\"begin\": 572, \"end\": 585, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alica_Schmidt\", \"score\": 0.9999999993119673, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alica Schmidt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alica_Schmidt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alica_Schmidt\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With over five millionInstagramfollowers, the 25-year-old athlete has garnered attention from high-end fashion houses, having worked withPuma, Nike and BOSS.\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 784, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 779, \"end\": 783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hugo_Boss\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.593288848169293e-17, \"text\": \"BOSS\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hugo_Boss\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hugo_Boss\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last year, Schmidt went the extra mile in her career, walking for BOSS in theirMilanshow, while simultaneously releasing a sportswear collaboration.\", \"from\": 786, \"to\": 934, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 797, \"end\": 804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Schmidt_camera\", \"score\": 0.9999856832811781, \"rank\": 1.4315597173999432e-05, \"text\": \"Schmidt\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Schmidt_camera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Schmidt_camera\"}, {\"begin\": 852, \"end\": 856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hugo_Boss\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.593288848169293e-17, \"text\": \"BOSS\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hugo_Boss\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hugo_Boss\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"2.Coco Gauff, Tennis  Known for her bright and bold looks on the court, American tennis star Coco Gauff brings vibrancy to more than just her game.\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 1083, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1008, \"end\": 1016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999750582669579, \"rank\": 1.5038992158962996e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1029, \"end\": 1039, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Coco Gauff\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gauff, 20, shot to fame following her historic defeat of Venus Williams at Wimbledon in 2019 when she was only 15.\", \"from\": 1085, \"to\": 1199, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1142, \"end\": 1156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Venus_Williams\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Venus Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Venus_Williams\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Venus_Williams\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The following year, Gauff became the second youngest US player to make the Olympic team.\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1288, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1253, \"end\": 1255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9935082083015226, \"rank\": 0.00533480446089494, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The young star was dubbed the tennis world's new fashion 'it girl' last year following her successful collaboration with New Balance.\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1423, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1411, \"end\": 1422, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Balance\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"New Balance\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Balance\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Balance\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her collection was innovative, taking inspiration from basketball shoes and incorporating a mid-cut that is rarely seen in tennis attire.\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1561, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gauff has single-handedly elevated tennis-core with cool street-style accents.\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1640, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"3.\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1644, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sha'Carri Richardson, Athletics  US track star Sha'Carri Richardson could be easy to miss, with her record times in the 100 and 200-metre sprints, but the 24-year-old makes sure she's noticed with her head-turning ensembles.\", \"from\": 1645, \"to\": 1869, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1645, \"end\": 1665, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sha'Carri Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\"}, {\"begin\": 1678, \"end\": 1680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9935082083015226, \"rank\": 0.00533480446089494, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1692, \"end\": 1712, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sha'Carri Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Recently photographed in a Ralph Lauren Collection bodysuit for Vogue's August cover, Richardson is known for bringing bold (if notgold) glamour and extravagance to every look, most notably through her nails.\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 2079, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1898, \"end\": 1910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"score\": 0.7268443698143106, \"rank\": 0.3758103406037